<html>
    <head></head>
	<style type="text/css">
				@media print {
						body {
							font-family: Calibri, Candara, Segoe, "Segoe UI", Optima, sans-serif;
							font-size: 8pt;
							line-height: 1.3;
							margin: 0;
							padding: 0;
						}
						h4 {
							font-size: 9pt;
							text-transform: uppercase;
							margin-top: 2pt;
							margin-bottom: 2pt;
						}
						table {
							width: 100%;
							border-top: 1pt solid #333;
							border-left: 1pt solid #333;
							border-spacing: 0;
							margin-top: 0;
							margin-bottom: 12pt;
						}
						table th, table td {
							border-right: 1pt solid #333;
							border-bottom: 1pt solid #333;
							padding: 3px;
							vertical-align: top;
						}
						table th {
							font-weight: bold;
						}
						#header {
							margin-bottom: 10pt;
						}
						#header img {
							width: 100%;
						}
						#footer {
							border-top: 1pt solid #fdc601;
							position: running(footer);
							text-align: left;
							padding: 0;
						}
						p.page {
							display: inline-block;
							float: left;
						}
			  
						.pagenumber:before {
							content: counter(page)
						}
						.pagecount:before {
							content: counter(pages)
						}
						.text-center {
							text-align: center;
						}
						.text-right {
							text-align: right;
						}
						
						.text-normal{
							font-weight: normal !important;
						}
						
						.clearfix{
							clear: both;
						}
						
						tr.active {
							background: #ccc;
						}
						tr.sub {
							background: #efefef;
						}
						.instructions-box h1 {
							text-align: center;
							margin-bottom: 10pt;
						}
						.page-break {
							display: block;
							page-break-before: always;
						}
						.page-break div:last-child {
							display: block;
							page-break-before: always;
						}
						
						#tbodyratingscale{
							border: 1px solid #000;
							text-align: center;
							padding: 8pt;
						}
						
						div.col-3{
							width: 30%;
							padding: 5pt;
							display: inline;
							font-size: 10pt;
							
						}
						
						
					}

	@page {
						size: 8.5in 11in;
						margin: 0.3in 0.3in 0.5in 0.3in;@bottom-center {
							content: element(footer)
						}
					}

				</style>
		<body>
			<div id="header">
				<img src="data:image/png;base64,"/>
			</div>
		   
			<h2 class="text-center">PERFORMANCE APPRAISAL REPORT FOR SUPPORT STAFF</h2>
			
			 <table>
				<tbody>
					<tr>
						<td width="25%">Coverage Period :</td>
						<th width="75%"></th>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>Department / Office :</td>
						<th></th>
					</tr>
					
					<tr>
						<td>Evaluatee Name :</td>
						<th></th>
					</tr>
				</tbody>
			</table>
		  
			<div id="divevaluationtool">IDdivevaluationtool</div>
			<table>
				<tbody>
					<tr>
						<th width="50%"><h2>TOTAL :</h2><br/><br/></th>
						
						<th width="50%"><h2>PERFORMANCE EQUIVALENT :</h2><br/><br/></th>
					</tr>
					
				 
				</tbody>
			</table>
			
			<h2>Rating Scale</h2>
			<div id="tbodyratingscale">
				IDtbodyratingscale
			</div>
			
			<div class="clearfix"></div>
			<h2>Development Action Plan</h2>
			<table>
				<tr>
					<th width="50%">STRENGTHS</th>
					<th width="50%">AREAS FOR IMPROVEMENT</th>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></td>
					<td><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<th width="50%">ACTION PLAN</th>
					<th width="50%">BY WHEN</th>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></td>
					<td><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<th width="50%" colspan="2">RECOMMENDED TRAININGS</th>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td colspan="2"><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></td>
				</tr>
			</table>
		</body>
	</html>
